{
  "stem": "1496.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had to decide to learn some kind of trade in order to survive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And being also mechanically-minded, I got myself a job as a machinist in a factory, and start learning how to be toolmaker, machines and toolmaker.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, the older brother, was working before the war, was working in a bank, because he also graduate this commercial high school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My younger brother was too young.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was only 12 years old, he was too young to do any work.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my both parents were very active in the business all the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother was also active in the business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Troyhandler, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She remained with my father, and other people remained in the business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was already like a forced labor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't part, because, again, I was working in my father's shop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then when I got a job in a factory as a machinist, this was already my job.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was lucky that I wasn't-- that was the main reason why I undertook this job as a machinist, because I felt that this might help me to stay away from these forced labor camps.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother, then, the older brother, he lost his job in the bank.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when the war started, he got a job in the-- as a carpenter-- cabinet maker in a factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he had to-- everybody had to find something to do, otherwise, the Nazis would take and send you away to some forced labor camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not paid at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We-- again, this was very short, because in 1941, the Nazis decided to create a ghetto in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this changed the whole situation.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
